OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWarm during
OL,6,Fthe evening, rather cloudy in the
OL,7,Fnorth and west, with spells of rain
OL,8,Fpossible here, perhaps interspersed by
OL,9,Fsome heavier and more showery bursts
OL,10,Flocally. Becoming generally drier with
OL,11,Fclearer periods developing during the
OL,12,Fearly hours.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FMainly fine with sunny spells
OL,15,Fintially, but tending to becoming
OL,16,Fcloudier from the northwest as
OL,17,Foccasional rain makes hesitant
OL,18,Fprogress eastwards, eventually heavier
OL,19,Fin places. Very warm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
