OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand damp for a time Saturday, but
OL,7,Fbecoming drier and brighter with sunny
OL,8,Fspells later in the weekend, ahead of
OL,9,Fisolated thunderstorms possible
OL,10,FMonday. Temperatures climbing, warm
OL,11,Fand humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
